taunts.immunity: does not practice the Kralien religion faithfully
taunts.text: Hey wormface! Can I borrow your Holy Scroll of Amborax? I need to wipe my stinky feet!

taunts.immunity: complained to Kralien High Command that Kralien ships are too weak
taunts.text: You call that a warship? I could crush that toy with my bare hands.
You're so ugly that your husband will thank me for killing you!

taunts.immunity: openly dislikes the Arvonian Royal Family
taunts.text: Queen Marah looks like a hideous pustule and smells like a flatulent Space Whale.
Your husband dresses like a Situlan scum slug!

taunts.immunity: does not care about space whales
taunts.text: I'll kill you later, Arvonian. Right now I'm enjoying a bowl of space whale soup.

taunts.immunity: runs a tidy ship and has no insecurity about hygiene
taunts.text: Do us all a favor and take a bath, you fungus-infested pachyderm!

taunts.immunity: has already mourned his dead mother and will not react to taunts about her
taunts.text: Your father is a Space Whale!

taunts.immunity: has the highest Torgoth efficiency rating and will not react to taunts about his ship's condition
taunts.text: That broken down rust bucket guarantees victory for Earth.
Your brother is a flea-bitten Matarian mule!

taunts.immunity: believes his ship is attractive and will not react to taunts about his ship's appearance
taunts.text: Your ship is so ugly my eyeballs burn just looking at it!

taunts.immunity: sometimes disagrees with Skaraan corporate leadership
taunts.text: Your corporate bosses are a bunch of money-losing morons!
We are not your enemy!
Please communicate with us.
